snippet: The U.N. nuclear watchdog sought in talks with Iran on Tuesday to advance a long-stalled investigation into Tehran's atomic activities, but it was not immediately clear whether any headway was made....

headline.print_headline: Iran and IAEA End Nuclear Talks, No Early Sign of Breakthrough
headline.main: Iran and IAEA End Nuclear Talks, No Early Sign of Breakthrough

lead_paragraph: The U.N. nuclear watchdog sought in talks with Iran on Tuesday to advance a long-stalled investigation into Tehran's atomic activities, but it was not immediately clear whether any headway was made.
